{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9eed91baa6","title":"右派言论——“唯心论的科学家照样可以搞出许多东西”","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选集》（天津：南开大学社会主义思想教育教研室，1957年9月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6c8fedc768","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"9eed91baa6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"d0a73efe7d","name":"王军庆"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8a507ce2b5","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“唯心论的科学家照样可以搞出许多东西”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"eef94da4c1","type":"authors","text":"南开大学王军庆","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"7f82ea2b70","type":"subtitle","text":"[王军庆：南开大学数学系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"2da6fdcddc","type":"paragraph","text":"“唯心论的科学家照样可以搞出许多东西。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"d38effeda5","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在学好功课，就等政治上的进步。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"919ac11698","type":"paragraph","text":"“只要有才，就是缺一点‘德’也不要紧。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"1981bbc595","type":"paragraph","text":"“只要不是反革命份子，缺点德没有关系。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"00e9de4b9b","type":"paragraph","text":"（在学习毛主席讲话时说）“学这个不能像学数学那样，如果学它能帮助我成为数学家，就可以好好学。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"6878ebef12","type":"paragraph","text":"“叶圣陶是从小学教师一步步升上去的，谁愿意去当清道夫，劳动是有等别的，有真才实学才有名望。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"fccf54514c","type":"paragraph","text":"“在今天这个社会里，反革命份子已经肃清，不为社会主义服务，也得为社会主义服务。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"755a969e75","type":"paragraph","text":"(他攻击毕业生分配工作说)“过去只考虑德，不考虑才。”“人事部门在分配时首先应该重才。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"883b346e6c","type":"paragraph","text":"“解放后没有出天才，这是由于教条主义束缚的结果，是由于组织意图强加于人们头上的结果。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"04df8def78","type":"paragraph","text":"×   ×   ×","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"ca8b30ead0","type":"paragraph","text":"“要想反三害，就必需反三害份子。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"afe9002097","type":"paragraph","text":"“官僚主义是和现行的一套机构的形式有关，在旧的形式上反对官僚主义是不可能成功的。”他认为“争自由、争人权、争民主”的大字报打中了要害，他说：“这一个问题要解决了，什么问题都解决了。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"badb61b065","type":"paragraph","text":"×   ×   ×","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"9ab5650571","type":"paragraph","text":"“取消党委负责制，并不等于取消党的领导，何况现在还未决定那种形式最好。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"e747d4c768","type":"paragraph","text":"“南开大学的党委水平低，跟不上形势的发展，应当改组。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"38a3ca4233","type":"paragraph","text":"“党委有无形的压制，这种无形压制比压制还坏。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"8a6a982fed","type":"paragraph","text":"“党委是靠党中央的威信吃饭的。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"b347d62046","type":"paragraph","text":"“数学系党支部不能体现无产阶级先进性。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"8ae5f3e9bf","type":"paragraph","text":"“党只关心党员，不关心青年前途。”","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"cb7f1eda02","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员都有靠山，不务正业，靠着党的威信吃饭。”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"6130d3590f","type":"paragraph","text":"“我班党员不用功，由于有‘党天下’思想，所以他们可以不务正业，也可以考虑他们的工作。”","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"d3f2df6b16","type":"paragraph","text":"“许多人是站在我的脖子上爬上去的，我恨的不是这些人！而是我系党团支持这样做，如任新渝就是郭先生捧上来的。”","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"1293f73a71","type":"paragraph","text":"“一些人踏在别人的肩膀上爬上去。”","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"3925d05a55","type":"paragraph","text":"“我班上没有社会主义的人与人之间的关系。”","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"b536408393","type":"paragraph","text":"“我相信世界上没有一个人是大公无私的，人不为己，天诛地灭。”","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"38bc58415a","type":"paragraph","text":"×   ×   ×","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"0dd5e34b7c","type":"paragraph","text":"“‘一株毒草’表现了谭天荣的天才和狂妄，勇敢和胡搞，是向三害发出的可贵的第一枪。天才和狂妄经常搅在一起，而天才是主要的。”","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"7af4182940","type":"paragraph","text":"×   ×   ×","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"},{"id":"c3e336bfff","type":"paragraph","text":"“为了精简机构，合并团委会，人事处，学生科，把多余的干部送到农村中去，反正报纸说参加生产是光荣的。”","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6"}],"page":{"id":"31f3f7db2a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"9eed91baa6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}